<br>
The formula for LH from levels 1-40 is (32L + 1) where L is your level.  The formula for 41-60 USED to be (1281 + (76 *(L-40))).  <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> It looks like they broke the 41+ formula and we are ALL getting the 32L+1 formula</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->.  <br>
<br>
The person who is 53 got a 1697 which happens to be 32 * 53 + 1. <br>
The person who is 57 got a 1825 which happens to be 32 * 57 + 1. <br>
A level 60 person would get 32*60+1 = 1921.<br>
<br>
